messages.messageBody:
http://www.unerzogen-magazin.de/archiv/?view=ad&aid=83&mid=5

If you have any friends or relatives who can read German or would like
to try, there's something.

It has been deposited (in its English original) in the upcoming Big Book
http://sandradodd.com/bigbook

And now I'm leaving to see Schuyler!! Holly made me a peanut butter
sandwich so she would know I wouldn't be hungry in the plane, and now
she's ready to drive me to the airport. HOW COOL! Very sweet of
her.


It will hardly seem that I'm gone, from the point of view of this
list, except posts might not be approved as quickly as if I were not
asleep on an airplane or being a happy tourist.

Don't forget Learn Nothing Day! Six days away. Learn a lot before
then so the day off won't put you behind!


Sandra
